1. *Pozovimo* prijatelje da se pridruže našoj zabavi. (Let's invite friends to join our party.)
2. Kada *pozovete* klijenta na sastanak, budite precizni oko vremena i lokacije. (When you invite a client to a meeting, be precise about the time and location.)
3. Oni će *pozivati* sve zainteresovane kandidate za posao. (They will be calling all interested job candidates.)
4. Da li si *pozvala* mamu da ti pomogne oko spremanja? (Did you call mom to help you with the cleaning?)
5. Neki ljudi se plaše *da pozovu* hitnu pomoć u slučaju zdravstvenih problema. (Some people are afraid to call an ambulance in case of health problems.)
6. *Pozvali* smo policiju kada smo primetili sumnjive aktivnosti u komšiluku. (We called the police when we noticed suspicious activity in the neighborhood.)
7. Kada se *pozoveš* na neki izvor u svom radu, obavezno navedi punu referencu. (When you cite a source in your work, always provide a full reference.)
8. Koliko ljudi si *pozvala* na svoj rođendanski party? (How many people did you invite to your birthday party?)
9. Molim vas da me *pozovete* čim stignete na aerodrom. (Please call me as soon as you arrive at the airport.)
10. Da li je neko već *pozvao* majstore da poprave krov? (Has anyone already called the repairmen to fix the roof?)